<section class="hero container fade-up">
  <p class="t-eyebrow hero__eyebrow">Framework 02 · The core</p>
  <h1 class="t-h1 hero__title t-balance">The Living System</h1>
  <p class="t-lead hero__lead t-pretty">A map of how soul, nervous system, body, mind, identity, relationships, and world continually shape one another.</p>
</section>

<section class="section section--sunk fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-2" style="align-items:center; gap: var(--sp-8);">
      <div class="clearing" style="width:100%">
        <div class="figure" style="aspect-ratio: 4/5; max-width: 460px; margin-inline: auto;">
          <img src="/assets/uploads/the-living-system.png" alt="A watercolor illustration of a tree labelled as one living system: mind, nervous system, and relations in the canopy; soul and identity among the branches; light and air flanking it; body at the trunk; and ancestry, soil, and water among the roots." loading="lazy" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stack-lg">
        <p class="t-lead t-pretty">Soul, mind, nervous system, body, identity, relationships — these are not the parts of you. They are the shapes life is taking in you, right now. Each one wants to belong; each one carries something the others cannot.</p>
        <p class="t-body t-pretty">What lives below — soil, water, ancestry — is no less you than what reaches toward the light. The roots are where the tree begins. You did not arrive in the world from nowhere; you grew here, out of all of this.</p>
        <p class="t-body t-pretty">Wholeness begins when nothing in you is left out. When the parts stop competing for who gets to be real, and the roots, trunk, and canopy remember they are one tree.</p>
        <p class="t-body t-pretty"><em>You are not separate from what you grow inside.</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section fade-up">
  <div class="container narrow center-text">
    <p class="pull t-balance"><em>A soul, in a body, in a nervous system, in a forest of other living systems.</em></p>
  </div>
</section>

